              <span id="reviewTextContainer1208744312" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1954653738628718124">overall a beautifully written novel. took me a bit to get through. a little long and slow to get going, but about halfway the pace picks up and is really interesting with twists and turns along the way.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


