      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2447331-a-quiet-belief-in-angels">Quotes from A Quiet Belief in...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
